  ('dietitian-moex-00219', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-114-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關糖尿病人的胰島素注射，下列敘述何者正確？', '["注射lispro胰島素的病人，應計算並教導他insulin to carbohydrate ratio", "晚上身體通常分泌較多的counterregulatory hormones，因此晚上的胰島素劑量通常高於早上", "注射premixed胰島素的病人，飲食較有彈性，能依生活上的變動，自由調整每餐的醣攝取量", "進行中度至強度的運動45～60分鐘，需減少1～2 units NPH胰島素注射"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:49+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7aa83b1fecb3", "answer_pdf_sha1": "65efadb3135a", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114030", "c": "102", "s": "0201", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 18, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
